Sales professionals can personalise every conversation and achieve 200% of their objectives by using personality insights from OrbitShift AI to discover the distinctive personality of the prospect. developing long-lasting, dependable relationships!


➤ Sales Professionals
OrbitShift won't just give you personalization tips as products like Crystal Knows or IBM Watson do, it will also predict their decision-making speed, risk-appetite, decision-factors and ability to say no. You will hit your targets in half the time!

By accurately predicting anyone's personality, without any tests, using just pre-existing data, OrbitShift AI will help you take the guesswork out of any interaction. Whether you are cold calling or reaching out via email , everything will start converting 2X more because of your unique, personalized approach.

Use OrbitShift seamlessly by installing our Chrome browser extension. This extension will allow you to easily retrieve your session cookies each time you use OrbitShift.

Here is what you can achieve by using OrbitShift:

- Collect additional lead information and create a link between platforms.
- Collect lead data from the web and connect with your leads on engagement platforms

How does this extension work?

This extension will automatically retrieve the session cookies of the websites you are connected to. Once you log into your OrbitShift account, click on “Connect to [website name] to fill out the session cookies input field. 

If you have any questions about this extension, feel free to send us an email to our support team at support@orbitshift.ai.
